Mlf4j CHANGELOG
========================
http://www.zollty.com/log-monitor/


Changes in version 1.0.0 (2014-05-08)
-------------------------------------
Create this project. log-monitor Mlf4j(Monitoring Logging Facade for Java) based on [zollty-log](http://www.zollty.com/zollty-log/), it's a facade or abstraction for various logging frameworks (e.g. java.util.logging, logback, log4j) allowing the end user to plug in the desired logging framework at deployment time. It is not only a facade, but also provides some useful decorations for common logging frameworks, such as log monitoring, online log viewer, configuration dynamic refreshing.

